  "text": "Data for ToxRead have been derived from the set of compounds available within VEGA [CITATION_1] . The source of these data has been described in the literature, referring to the VEGA models on BCF [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] ; basically they derive from data considered of good quality, such as the EURAS database [17] , with the addition of further compounds from the literature [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] . When multiple data for the same compounds were available the arithmetic mean value was used in the database for the read-across. In total there are 860 chemicals in the database supporting the read-across.",
